npm init
mpm init -y
npm install packageName or npm i packageName
npm install packageName -save
npm list

a) Install EJS
npm i ejs -save
b) Create views folder in Application folder
c) Set view engine in ritik.js
app.set('view engine', 'ejs');
d) instead of send use render (res.render('viewName')

How to add Images/CSS/JS in Express Project

a) Create public folder in Application folder
b) Create images folder in public folder

c) Create stylesheets folder in public folder
d) Create style1.css inside folder stylesheets
e) Open "header.ejs" file and link "style1.css" file
<link href="stylesheets/style1.css" rel="stylesheet" >
